## 3. 完整狀態流轉

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
  ready_for_assignment --> draft_round: 產生排組
  draft_round --> locked: 🔒 鎖定開打
  locked --> in_progress: (自動) Session 狀態
  locked --> finished: ✓ 結束本輪
  finished --> round_finished: (自動) Session 狀態
  round_finished --> draft_round: ➕ 排下一輪
  round_finished --> session_finished: 🏁 結束場次
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 當第一輪鎖定時，`lock_round_and_increment_counters` RPC 會自動觸發 `charge_session_first_start`（首次扣費邏輯），確保計費只發生一次。

